data.title: Dallas Regional Service Center
data.text:
Make an Appointment

NEW: At certain locations, dealers, title service companies, and their runners are eligible to book appointments by selecting ‘Motor Vehicle Dealers’ or ‘Title Companies and Runners’ from the Appointment Type menu on the appointment page.

At all other locations, dealers, title service companies, and their runners are not eligible to book appointments.

Some offices may limit the quantity of transactions which may be processed at one time by these entities.
